(5457, '16', 'I am the master of whisperers.', 9),
(5458, '160', 'That should get young Joffrey\'s attention.', 9),
(5459, '161', 'And it, uh, puts a thousand leagues between you and Thorne.', 9),
(5460, '162', 'Now go and put your sword somewhere safe...', 9),
