(11155, '330', '- She was a good... - She\'s dead.', 17),
(11156, '331', 'She died alone. She died for me and I couldn\'t protect her.', 17),
(11157, '332', 'Doreah?', 17),
(11158, '333', 'We can\'t find her.', 17),
(11159, '334', 'She must be dead, too.', 17),
(11160, '335', 'I led my people out of the Red Waste and into the slaughterhouse.', 17),
(11161, '336', 'I should have been here.', 17),
(11162, '337', 'You went to find me a ship.', 17),
(11163, '338', 'My place is by your side.', 17),
(11164, '339', 'I shouldn\'t have left you alone with these people.', 17),
(11165, '34', 'It\'s all just a game.', 17),
