(14233, '565', 'They may suit my needs. Tell me of their training.', 21),
(14234, '566', 'The Westerosi woman is pleased with them,', 21),
(14235, '567', 'but speaks no praise to keep the price down.', 21),
(14236, '568', 'She wishes to know how they are trained.', 21),
(14237, '569', 'Tell her what she would know and be quick about it.', 21),
(14238, '57', 'From now on, you\'d better kneel every time I fart.', 21),
