(14243, '574', 'the shield, and the three spears.', 21),
(14244, '575', 'Only one boy in four survives this rigorous training.', 21),
(14245, '576', 'Their discipline and loyalty are absolute.', 21),
(14246, '577', 'They fear nothing.', 21),
(14247, '578', 'Even the bravest men fear death.', 21),
(14248, '579', 'The knight says even brave men fear death.', 21),
(14249, '58', 'Stand, boy.', 21),
(14250, '580', 'Tell the old man he smells of piss.', 21),
(14251, '581', 'Truly, Master?', 21),
(14252, '582', 'No, not truly.', 21),
(14253, '583', 'Are you a girl or a goat to ask such a thing?', 21),
(14254, '584', 'My master says the Unsullied are not men. Death means nothing to them.', 21),
(14255, '585', 'Tell this ignorant whore of a Westerner', 21),
(14256, '586', 'to open her eyes and watch.', 21),
(14257, '587', 'He begs you attend to this carefully, Your Grace.', 21),
(14258, '588', 'Tell the good master there is no need.', 21),
(14259, '589', 'She\'s worried about their nipples?', 21),
(14260, '59', 'We don\'t kneel for anyone beyond the Wall.', 21),
(14261, '590', 'Does the dumb bitch know we\'ve cut off their balls?', 21),
(14262, '591', 'My master points out that men don\'t need nipples.', 21),
(14263, '592', 'Here, I\'m done with you.', 21),
(14264, '593', 'This one is pleased to have served you.', 21),
(14265, '594', 'To win his shield,', 21),
(14266, '595', 'an Unsullied must go to the slave marts with a silver mark,', 21),
(14267, '596', 'find a newborn and kill it before its mother\'s eyes.', 21),
(14268, '597', 'This way, my master says, we make certain', 21),
(14269, '598', 'there is no weakness left in them.', 21),
(14270, '599', 'You take a babe from its mother\'s arms,', 21),
(14271, '6', 'That was your job.', 21),
(14272, '60', 'So, you\'re Ned Stark\'s bastard.', 21),
(14273, '600', 'kill it as she watches, and pay for her pain with a silver coin?', 21),
(14274, '601', 'She is offended.', 21),
(14275, '602', 'She asks if you pay a silver coin to the mother,', 21),
(14276, '603', 'for her dead baby.', 21),
(14277, '604', 'What a soft mewling fool this one is.', 21),
(14278, '605', 'My master would like you to know that the silver is paid', 21),
(14279, '606', 'to the baby\'s owner, not the mother.', 21),
(14280, '607', 'How many do you have to sell?', 21),
(14281, '608', 'Eight thousand.', 21),
(14282, '609', 'Tell the Westerosi whore she has until tomorrow.', 21),
(14283, '61', 'Thank you for the gift, Lord of Bones. You can leave us.', 21),
