(14285, '611', 'Many other buyers are interested.', 21),
(14286, '612', 'Eight thousand dead babies.', 21),
(14287, '613', 'The Unsullied are a means to an end.', 21),
(14288, '614', 'Once I own them, these men...', 21),
(14289, '615', 'They\'re not men. Not any more.', 21),
(14290, '616', 'Once I own an army of slaves, what will I be?', 21),
(14291, '617', 'You think these slaves will have better lives', 21),
(14292, '618', 'serving men like Kraznys or serving you?', 21),
(14293, '619', 'You\'ll be fair to them. You won\'t mutilate them to make a point.', 21),
(14294, '62', 'The girl likes you.', 21),
(14295, '620', 'You won\'t order them to murder babies.', 21),
(14296, '621', 'You\'ll see they\'re properly fed and sheltered.', 21),
(14297, '622', 'A great injustice has been done to them.', 21),
(14298, '623', 'Closing your eyes will not undo it.', 21),
(14299, '624', 'The warlocks.', 21),
(14300, '625', 'I owe you my life, ser.', 21),
(14301, '626', 'The honour is mine, my queen.', 21),
(14302, '627', 'You know this man?', 21),
(14303, '628', 'I know him', 21),
(14304, '629', 'as one of the greatest fighters', 21),
(14305, '63', 'You like her back, Snow?', 21),
(14306, '630', 'the Seven Kingdoms has ever seen', 21),
(14307, '631', 'and as the Lord Commander of Robert Baratheon\'s Kingsguard.', 21),
(14308, '632', 'King Robert is dead.', 21),
(14309, '633', 'I have been searching for you, Daenerys Stormborn, to ask your forgiveness.', 21),
(14310, '634', 'I was sworn to protect your family.', 21),
(14311, '635', 'I failed them.', 21),
(14312, '636', 'I am Barristan Selmy, Kingsguard to your father.', 21),
(14313, '637', 'Allow me to join your Queensguard and I will not fail you again.', 21),
(14314, '64', 'That why you want to join us?', 21),
(14315, '65', 'Don\'t panic, boy.', 21),
(14316, '66', 'This isn\'t the damned Night\'s Watch', 21),
(14317, '67', 'where we make you swear off girls.', 21),
(14318, '68', 'This chicken eater you thought was king is Tormund Giantsbane.', 21),
(14319, '69', 'Can\'t believe this pup killed the Halfhand.', 21),
(14320, '7', 'Your only job.', 21),
(14321, '70', 'He was our enemy', 21),
(14322, '71', 'and I\'m glad he\'s dead.', 21),
(14323, '72', 'He was my brother once.', 21),
(14324, '73', 'Back when he had a whole hand.', 21),
(14325, '74', 'What were you doing with him?', 21),
(14326, '75', 'The Lord Commander sent me to the Halfhand for seasoning.', 21),
(14327, '76', 'Why?', 21),
(14328, '77', 'He wants me to lead one day.', 21),
(14329, '78', 'But here you are, a traitor,', 21),
(14330, '79', 'kneeling before the King-beyond-the-Wall.', 21),
(14331, '8', 'We need to get back to the Wall.', 21),
(14332, '80', 'If I\'m a traitor, then you are, too.', 21),
(14333, '81', 'Why do you want to join us, Jon Snow?', 21),
(14334, '82', 'I want to be free.', 21),
(14335, '83', 'No, I don\'t think so.', 21),
(14336, '84', 'I think what you want most of all is to be a hero.', 21),
(14337, '85', 'I\'ll ask you one last time,', 21),
(14338, '86', 'why do you want to join us?', 21),
(14339, '87', 'We stopped at Craster\'s Keep on the way north.', 21),
(14340, '88', 'I saw...', 21),
