(14342, '9', 'It\'s a long march.', 21),
(14343, '90', 'I saw Craster take his own baby boy and leave it in the woods.', 21),
(14344, '91', 'I saw what took it.', 21),
(14345, '92', 'You\'re telling me you saw one of them?', 21),
(14346, '93', 'And why would that make you desert your brothers?', 21),
(14347, '94', 'Because when I told the Lord Commander,', 21),
(14348, '95', 'he already knew.', 21),
(14349, '96', 'Thousands of years ago, the First Men defeated the White Walkers.', 21),
(14350, '97', 'I want to fight for the side that fights for the living.', 21),
(14351, '98', 'Did I come to the right place?', 21),
(14352, '99', 'We\'ll need to find you a new cloak.', 21),
(14353, '1', 'Don\'t think too much, Bran.', 22),
(14354, '10', 'Hodor.', 22),
(14355, '100', 'Did you ever tell him? No, of course not.', 22),
(14356, '101', 'You weren\'t Renly\'s type, I\'m afraid.', 22),
(14357, '102', 'He preferred curly-haired little girls like Loras Tyrell.', 22),
(14358, '103', 'You\'re far too much man for him.', 22),
(14359, '104', 'I\'m not interested in foul rumours.', 22),
(14360, '105', 'Unless they\'re about me.', 22),
(14361, '106', 'It\'s all true about Renly.', 22),
(14362, '107', 'His proclivities were the worst kept secret at court.', 22),
(14363, '108', 'It\'s a shame the throne isn\'t made out of cocks.', 22),
(14364, '109', 'They\'d have never got him off it.', 22),
(14365, '11', 'Were you inside the wolf again, little lord?', 22),
(14366, '110', 'Shut your mouth!', 22),
(14367, '111', 'I don\'t blame him. And I don\'t blame you, either.', 22),
(14368, '112', 'We don\'t get to choose who we love.', 22),
(14369, '113', 'Where are you headed, then?', 22),
(14370, '114', 'South.', 22),
(14371, '115', '- You? - Riverrun.', 22),
