(14376, '12', 'No, it was the three-eyed raven.', 22),
(14377, '120', 'Looks like you\'re safe enough.', 22),
(14378, '121', 'Meaning no offence, my lady, but I wouldn\'t tangle with you.', 22),
(14379, '122', '- Seven blessings to you. - And you.', 22),
(14380, '123', 'He knows who I am.', 22),
