(14386, '129', 'Make it tighter here.', 22),
(14387, '13', 'He\'s back.', 22),
(14388, '130', 'Mmm. That\'s better.', 22),
(14389, '131', 'It makes you look very strong.', 22),
(14390, '132', 'No flowers.', 22),
(14391, '133', 'I said no flowers.', 22),
(14392, '134', 'All these are wrong. Bring others.', 22),
(14393, '135', 'Yes, Your Grace.', 22),
(14394, '136', 'Bloody flowers. On the king.', 22),
(14395, '137', 'Looks like a Tyrell rose. Give it to Margaery for her wedding gown.', 22),
(14396, '138', 'Should be more than enough fabric.', 22),
(14397, '139', 'Tell me what you think of her.', 22),
(14398, '14', 'I tried to kill it, but I couldn\'t.', 22),
(14399, '140', 'Who?', 22),
(14400, '141', 'Margaery.', 22),
(14401, '142', 'She\'s an ideal match.', 22),
(14402, '143', 'With the Tyrells beside us, we\'ll crush the Northerners.', 22),
(14403, '144', 'Hang their lords, burn their strongholds, sow their fields with salt,', 22),
(14404, '145', 'and no one will think of rebelling for another century.', 22),
(14405, '146', 'It is a good match, but what do you think of her?', 22),
(14406, '147', 'She\'s beautiful and intelligent.', 22),
(14407, '148', 'Yes, she is.', 22),
(14408, '149', 'Her concern with the well-being', 22),
(14409, '15', '- There was a boy. - I don\'t want to hear about it.', 22),
(14410, '150', 'of the common people is interesting.', 22),
(14411, '151', 'Not to me.', 22),
(14412, '152', 'I only meant to go out of your way to endanger...', 22),
(14413, '153', 'This is becoming one of the most boring conversations I\'ve ever had.', 22),
(14414, '154', 'Margaery Tyrell dotes on filthy urchins for a reason.', 22),
(14415, '155', 'She dresses like a harlot for a reason.', 22),
(14416, '156', 'Married a traitor and known degenerate', 22),
(14417, '157', 'like Renly Baratheon for a reason.', 22),
(14418, '158', 'She married Renly Baratheon because she was told to.', 22),
(14419, '159', 'That\'s what intelligent women do. What they\'re told.', 22),
(14420, '16', '- But you asked. - We\'ve got plenty of worries.', 22),
(14421, '160', 'You need to ask yourself...', 22),
(14422, '161', 'I don\'t need to do anything.', 22),
(14423, '162', 'Better.', 22),
(14424, '163', 'Much better.', 22),
(14425, '164', 'I still don\'t believe it.', 22),
(14426, '165', 'He didn\'t want anything.', 22),
(14427, '166', 'He just takes an interest because he loved my mother.', 22),
(14428, '167', 'Men only want one thing from a pretty girl.', 22),
(14429, '168', 'Littlefinger\'s not in love with me.', 22),
(14430, '169', 'Love is not the thing he wants.', 22),
(14431, '17', 'We don\'t need to pour black magic on top of them.', 22),
(14432, '170', 'He\'s too old.', 22),
(14433, '171', 'They never see it that way.', 22),
(14434, '172', 'He didn\'t ask you to do something for him?', 22),
(14435, '173', 'Spy on someone or...', 22),
(14436, '174', 'No.', 22),
(14437, '175', 'If he does ask you for anything or try anything', 22),
(14438, '176', 'or touch you, I want you to tell me.', 22),
(14439, '177', 'Why? What will you do?', 22),
(14440, '178', 'I will make him stop.', 22),
(14441, '179', 'Ser Loras Tyrell, my lady.', 22),
(14442, '18', 'I didn\'t ask for black magic dreams.', 22),
(14443, '180', 'Send him in.', 22),
(14444, '181', 'Lady Sansa.', 22),
(14445, '182', 'Ser Loras.', 22),
(14446, '183', 'My sister invites you to take the air with her and our grandmother,', 22),
(14447, '184', 'the Lady Olenna, in the gardens.', 22),
(14448, '185', 'May I escort you to them?', 22),
(14449, '186', 'I believe you grow more beautiful every day, Lady Sansa.', 22),
(14450, '187', 'You are too kind, Ser Loras.', 22),
(14451, '188', 'You probably don\'t remember the first time we met.', 22),
(14452, '189', 'At the Hand\'s tourney, you gave me your favour.', 22),
(14453, '19', 'I know you didn\'t, little lord.', 22),
(14454, '190', 'A rose, a red rose.', 22),
