(25172, '586', 'before killing her, too.', 37),
(25173, '587', 'I will be your champion.', 37),
(25174, '588', 'Hello, Robin.', 37),
(25175, '589', 'What are you doing?', 37),
(25176, '59', 'Welcome to the capital.', 37),
(25177, '590', 'I\'m building my home, Winterfell.', 37),
(25178, '591', 'At least I think I am. I haven\'t been back there in a very long time.', 37),
(25179, '592', 'Why did you leave?', 37),
(25180, '593', 'It\'s a long story.', 37),
(25181, '594', 'I stay here in the Eyrie.', 37),
(25182, '595', 'Mother says it\'s dangerous on the roads and I have to keep myself safe', 37),
(25183, '596', 'because I\'m the Lord of the Vale', 37),
(25184, '597', 'and a very important person.', 37),
(25185, '598', 'Yes, you certainly are.', 37),
(25186, '599', 'When will you go back?', 37),
(25187, '6', 'It\'s not a joke. You understand that, don\'t you?', 37),
(25188, '60', 'Thank you for riding here so quickly.', 37),
(25189, '600', 'Probably never.', 37),
(25190, '601', 'My family doesn\'t live there any more and someone burned it down.', 37),
(25191, '602', 'Oh.', 37),
(25192, '603', 'Does Winterfell have a Moon Door?', 37),
(25193, '604', 'No, I\'m afraid not.', 37),
(25194, '605', 'It\'s not high up in the mountains. It\'s down on the ground.', 37),
(25195, '606', 'That sounds dangerous.', 37),
(25196, '607', '- How do you make people fly? - We don\'t.', 37),
(25197, '608', 'What do you do with all the bad people', 37),
(25198, '609', 'and the scary people and the people you don\'t like?', 37),
(25199, '61', 'You seem to be in good form.', 37),
(25200, '610', 'I never did anything with them at all.', 37),
(25201, '611', 'Girls didn\'t take part in that where I came from.', 37),
(25202, '612', 'Well, I\'m Lord of the Vale.', 37),
(25203, '613', 'When I grow up, I\'ll be able to fly anybody who bothers me.', 37),
(25204, '614', 'Or you. When we get married,', 37),
(25205, '615', 'you can tell me if you don\'t like somebody', 37),
(25206, '616', 'and then we can bring them back here and, whoosh!', 37),
(25207, '617', 'Right through the Moon Door.', 37),
(25208, '618', 'I like the sound of that.', 37),
(25209, '619', 'Let\'s put a Moon Door in your Winterfell.', 37),
(25210, '62', 'Who am I fighting?', 37),
(25211, '620', 'All right.', 37),
(25212, '621', '- It can go in here in this big tower. - Be careful.', 37),
(25213, '622', 'You\'ve ruined it. Now I\'m going to have to rebuild the whole thing.', 37),
(25214, '623', '- I didn\'t ruin it. - You did.', 37),
(25215, '624', 'It was already ruined because it didn\'t have a Moon Door.', 37),
(25216, '625', '- I was fixing it. - Knocking things down isn\'t fixing them.', 37),
(25217, '626', '- It\'s ruining them. - I didn\'t ruin it!', 37),
(25218, '627', '- You\'re being stupid. - I didn\'t ruin it!', 37),
(25219, '628', 'Robin, I\'m sorry, I...', 37),
(25220, '629', 'Children.', 37),
(25221, '63', 'Does it matter?', 37),
(25222, '630', '- I hit him. - Yes, I saw.', 37),
(25223, '631', '- I shouldn\'t have done that. - No.', 37),
(25224, '632', 'His mother should have, a long time ago.', 37),
(25225, '633', 'Consider it a step in the right direction.', 37),
(25226, '634', 'If he tells Aunt Lysa...', 37),
(25227, '635', 'Let me worry about Aunt Lysa.', 37),
(25228, '636', 'I was trying to remember what everything looked like.', 37),
(25229, '637', 'I\'ll never see it again.', 37),
(25230, '638', 'A lot can happen between now and never.', 37),
(25231, '639', 'If you want to build a better home,', 37),
(25232, '64', 'Could be food.', 37),
(25233, '640', 'first you must demolish the old one.', 37),
(25234, '641', 'Why did you really kill Joffrey?', 37),
(25235, '642', 'Tell me why.', 37),
(25236, '643', 'I loved your mother more than you could ever know.', 37),
(25237, '644', 'Given the opportunity,', 37),
(25238, '645', 'what do we do to those who\'ve hurt the ones we love?', 37),
(25239, '646', 'In a better world,', 37),
(25240, '647', 'one where love could overcome strength and duty,', 37),
(25241, '648', 'you might have been my child.', 37),
(25242, '649', 'But we don\'t live in that world.', 37),
(25243, '65', 'Could be soldiers.', 37),
(25244, '650', 'You\'re more beautiful than she ever was.', 37),
(25245, '651', 'Lord Baelish...', 37),
(25246, '652', 'Call me Petyr.', 37),
(25247, '653', 'You wanted to see me, Aunt Lysa?', 37),
(25248, '654', 'Come here, Sansa.', 37),
(25249, '655', 'Do you know how far the fall is?', 37),
(25250, '656', 'No.', 37),
(25251, '657', 'Neither do I, precisely.', 37),
(25252, '658', 'Hundreds of feet.', 37),
(25253, '659', 'It\'s fascinating', 37),
(25254, '66', 'You shouldn\'t be sitting out here like this.', 37),
(25255, '660', 'what happens to bodies when they hit the rocks from such a height.', 37),
(25256, '661', 'The impact breaks them right apart.', 37),
(25257, '662', 'Like eggs dropped on the floor.', 37),
(25258, '663', 'Sometimes pieces remain intact.', 37),
(25259, '664', 'You\'ll find the head sitting on its own.', 37),
(25260, '665', 'Every hair in place.', 37),
(25261, '666', 'Blue eyes staring at nothing.', 37),
(25262, '667', 'I know what you did.', 37),
(25263, '668', 'I\'m so sorry, Aunt Lysa.', 37),
(25264, '669', 'I never should have hit Robin.', 37),
(25265, '67', 'Where else to sit?', 37),
(25266, '670', '- I promise it won\'t happen... - Don\'t be coy with me, you little whore.', 37),
(25267, '671', 'You kissed Petyr.', 37),
(25268, '672', '- I didn\'t. You don\'t understand. - I saw you.', 37),
(25269, '673', 'You can\'t lie to me because I saw it with my own eyes.', 37),
(25270, '674', '- He kissed me. I pulled away. - Liar! Whore!', 37),
(25271, '675', 'He is mine!', 37),
(25272, '676', 'My father, my husband, my sister,', 37),
(25273, '677', 'they all stood between us and now they\'re all dead.', 37),
(25274, '678', 'That\'s what happens to people who stand between Petyr and me.', 37),
(25275, '679', 'Look down!', 37),
(25276, '68', 'Tried to walk back to me hut,', 37),
(25277, '680', '- Look down! - Lysa!', 37),
(25278, '681', 'Let her go.', 37),
(25279, '682', 'You want her?', 37),
(25280, '683', 'This empty-headed child?', 37),
(25281, '684', 'Let her go.', 37),
(25282, '685', 'She\'s just like her mother. She\'ll never love you.', 37),
(25283, '686', 'I lied for you. I killed for you.', 37),
(25284, '687', '- Why did you bring her here? - I\'ll send her away.', 37),
(25285, '688', 'I swear on my life.', 37),
(25286, '689', 'I swear to all the gods.', 37),
(25287, '69', 'hurt too much.', 37),
(25288, '690', 'Let her go, Lysa.', 37),
(25289, '691', 'Oh, my sweet wife.', 37),
(25290, '692', 'My sweet, silly wife.', 37),
(25291, '693', 'I have only loved one woman,', 37),
(25292, '694', 'only one, my entire life.', 37),
(25293, '695', 'Your sister.', 37),
(25294, '7', 'Of course it\'s a joke, just not a very funny one.', 37),
(25295, '70', 'Then I remembered they burned me hut down.', 37),
(25296, '71', 'Who were \"they\"?', 37),
(25297, '72', 'I stopped asking a while ago.', 37),
(25298, '73', 'That\'s not going to get better.', 37),
(25299, '74', 'Doesn\'t seem so.', 37),
(25300, '75', 'A bad way to go.', 37);
INSERT INTO `subtitle` (`id`, `number`, `content`, `episode_id`) VALUES
(25301, '76', 'Haven\'t you had enough?', 37),
