(25380, '147', 'I swear it by the Drowned God.', 38),
(25381, '148', 'What is dead may never die.', 38),
(25382, '149', 'What is dead may never die.', 38),
(25383, '15', 'Woke me up.', 38),
(25384, '150', 'And if you were my prince,', 38),
(25385, '151', 'why are you marching with a Bolton army?', 38),
(25386, '152', 'Lord Bolton took me captive after Winterfell.', 38),
(25387, '153', 'He sent me to treat with you in good faith as your fellow ironborn.', 38),
(25388, '154', 'And what does Lord Bolton want?', 38),
(25389, '155', 'You are fading from sickness,', 38),
(25390, '156', 'you are badly outnumbered, and you\'re hundreds of miles from the sea.', 38),
(25391, '157', 'Lord Bolton implores you to protect your men', 38),
(25392, '158', 'and abandon this fortress you can no longer hold.', 38),
(25393, '159', 'Do this, and he will be just and fair with you as he has been with me.', 38),
(25394, '16', '- You hear me? - Yes.', 38),
(25395, '160', 'The Boltons will give you safe passage to the Stony Shore.', 38),
(25396, '161', 'He wants us to surrender?', 38),
(25397, '162', 'My own father, your king,', 38),
(25398, '163', 'surrendered years ago to Robert Baratheon.', 38),
(25399, '164', 'I watched him bend the knee.', 38),
(25400, '165', 'There was no shame there.', 38),
(25401, '166', 'He fought with honour, as did you.', 38),
(25402, '167', '\"No shame.\" \"Fought with honour.\"', 38),
(25403, '168', 'I\'m sorry, I didn\'t hear.', 38),
(25404, '169', '\"No shame.\" \"Fought with honour.\"', 38),
(25405, '17', 'Well, got anything to say?', 38),
(25406, '170', 'Only a whipped dog would speak this way.', 38),
(25407, '171', 'Or a woman.', 38),
(25408, '172', 'Are you a woman, boy?', 38),
(25409, '173', 'You don\'t know...', 38),
(25410, '174', 'The ironborn will not surrender.', 38),
(25411, '175', 'My name is Reek...', 38),
(25412, '176', 'You go tell your master that, Theon Greyjoy,', 38),
(25413, '177', 'or whoever the fuck you are.', 38),
(25414, '178', 'Reek.', 38),
(25415, '179', '- What in the hell are you muttering? - Reek.', 38),
(25416, '18', 'I\'m sorry.', 38),
(25417, '180', 'Reek.', 38),
(25418, '181', 'If we yield, we live?', 38),
(25419, '182', '- Is that what it says on this paper here? - Yes.', 38),
(25420, '183', 'Have your men raise the white flag and open the gates.', 38),
(25421, '184', 'You\'re going home.', 38),
(25422, '185', 'You didn\'t really think I\'d let them go, did you?', 38),
(25423, '186', 'It\'s fallen out of fashion, flaying.', 38),
(25424, '187', 'Sad, but true.', 38),
(25425, '188', 'Traditions are important.', 38),
(25426, '189', 'Where are we without our history? Eh?', 38),
(25427, '19', 'I don\'t care if you\'re sorry.', 38),
(25428, '190', 'Yes, my lord.', 38),
(25429, '191', 'Will we go home now?', 38),
(25430, '192', 'I believe we will.', 38),
(25431, '193', 'To our new home.', 38),
(25432, '194', 'You have foreign blood, don\'t you, Baelish?', 38),
(25433, '195', 'A great-grandfather from Braavos, yes.', 38),
(25434, '196', 'I suppose all of our ancestors came from somewhere else originally.', 38),
(25435, '197', 'Our forebears settled the Vale thousands of years ago.', 38),
(25436, '198', 'We\'ve fought off invaders ever since.', 38),
(25437, '199', 'The beauty of the Vale is matched only by the nobility of its great families.', 38),
(25438, '2', 'Ready?', 38),
(25439, '20', 'Keep that baby quiet, or I will.', 38),
(25440, '200', 'Lady Arryn often told me that you were her rock, Lord Royce.', 38),
(25441, '201', 'She told me nothing about you, Baelish.', 38),
(25442, '202', 'But I didn\'t need to hear from her.', 38),
(25443, '203', 'Moneylender. Whoremonger.', 38),
(25444, '204', 'You\'ve been licking Tywin Lannister\'s boots so long,', 38),
(25445, '205', '- it\'s a wonder your tongue\'s not black. - My lord...', 38),
(25446, '206', 'And when Jon Arryn named you Master of Coin, no one cared.', 38),
(25447, '207', 'Always been a grubby job. Why not let a grubby man do it?', 38),
(25448, '208', 'But when I heard you were lurking here,', 38),
(25449, '209', '- fawning over the Lady Arryn... - Lady Arryn invited me.', 38),
(25450, '21', 'Don\'t you ever touch him.', 38),
(25451, '210', 'She and I have been close since childhood.', 38),
(25452, '211', 'Yes, we all know how close you were.', 38),
(25453, '212', 'Lady Arryn\'s predilections were her own affair.', 38),
