(25455, '214', 'Of course. Her suicide shattered us all.', 38),
(25456, '215', 'She was an odd fish. Everyone knew that.', 38),
(25457, '216', 'But suicide?', 38),
(25458, '217', 'She adored that boy of hers.', 38),
(25459, '218', 'I don\'t see her abandoning him. Not by choice.', 38),
